{"words":[{"word":"team","count":5},{"word":"playername","count":5},{"word":"record","count":5},{"word":"relay","count":4},{"word":"general","count":4},{"word":"first","count":3},{"word":"runner","count":3},{"word":"perfect","count":2},{"word":"teammates","count":2},{"word":"said","count":2},{"word":"able","count":2},{"word":"participate","count":2},{"word":"temporary","count":2},{"word":"gulpuff","count":2},{"word":"race","count":2},{"word":"thank","count":2},{"word":"big","count":2},{"word":"jiyan","count":2},{"word":"ten","count":2},{"word":"years","count":2},{"word":"set","count":2},{"word":"since","count":2},{"word":"time","count":2},{"word":"hi","count":1},{"word":"wenshu","count":1},{"word":"timing","count":1},{"word":"bit","count":1},{"word":"situation","count":1},{"word":"two","count":1},{"word":"accidentally","count":1},{"word":"injured","count":1},{"word":"warm-up","count":1},{"word":"luckily","count":1},{"word":"wounds","count":1},{"word":"bad","count":1},{"word":"doctor","count":1},{"word":"anytime","count":1},{"word":"soon","count":1},{"word":"asked","count":1},{"word":"organizing","count":1},{"word":"committee","count":1},{"word":"speaking","count":1},{"word":"simple","count":1},{"word":"four","count":1},{"word":"people","count":1},{"word":"take","count":1},{"word":"turns","count":1},{"word":"controlling","count":1},{"word":"reach","count":1},{"word":"finish","count":1},{"word":"line","count":1},{"word":"wins","count":1},{"word":"prize","count":1},{"word":"money","count":1},{"word":"definitely","count":1},{"word":"split","count":1},{"word":"rank","count":1},{"word":"treat","count":1},{"word":"feast","count":1},{"word":"jinzhou","count":1},{"word":"favor","count":1},{"word":"oh","count":1},{"word":"mean","count":1},{"word":"counting","count":1},{"word":"greetings","count":1},{"word":"party","count":1},{"word":"pooper","count":1},{"word":"last-minute","count":1},{"word":"probably","count":1},{"word":"hit","count":1},{"word":"unless","count":1},{"word":"uh","count":1},{"word":"sorry","count":1},{"word":"forget","count":1},{"word":"ago","count":1},{"word":"remains","count":1},{"word":"unbeaten","count":1},{"word":"day","count":1},{"word":"every","count":1},{"word":"games","count":1},{"word":"held","count":1},{"word":"major","count":1},{"word":"highlight","count":1},{"word":"whether","count":1},{"word":"broken","count":1},{"word":"must","count":1},{"word":"trained","count":1},{"word":"together","count":1},{"word":"long","count":1},{"word":"learn","count":1},{"word":"anyway","count":1},{"word":"wonder","count":1},{"word":"team's","count":1},{"word":"ah","count":1},{"word":"order","count":1},{"word":"used","count":1},{"word":"decided","count":1},{"word":"captain","count":1},{"word":"decide","count":1},{"word":"alright","count":1},{"word":"case","count":1},{"word":"ganquan","count":1},{"word":"always","count":1},{"word":"training","count":1},{"word":"surely","count":1},{"word":"good","count":1},{"word":"start","count":1},{"word":"hmm","count":1},{"word":"connecting","count":1},{"word":"third","count":1},{"word":"familiar","count":1},{"word":"midnight","count":1},{"word":"rangers","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Hi, Wenshu! And this is...?","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Perfect timing! We're have a bit of a situation right now.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Two of our teammates accidentally injured themselves during warm-up... Luckily, the wounds weren't too bad, but the doctor said that they wouldn't be able to participate in the relay anytime soon.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"We've asked the organizing committee. Said we can still participate with temporary teammates.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Speaking of which... Do you have a team, {PlayerName}?","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"It's simple! Four people take turns controlling a Gulpuff in a relay race. The first team to reach the finish line wins.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Thank you so much! If we can get the prize money, we'll definitely split it with you!","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Even if we don't rank, we'll treat you to a big feast in Jinzhou to thank you for doing us such a big favor.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Oh! Why didn't I think of him!","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"What do you mean?","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"We're counting on you, {PlayerName}!","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Greetings, General Jiyan, {PlayerName}.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Not to be the party pooper here, but as a last-minute team, we probably won't hit the record. Unless...","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Uh, sorry, forget about it.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Ten years ago, a team set the record in the Gulpuff Relay race. That record remains unbeaten to this day.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Since then, every time the Games are held, a major highlight is whether the record will be broken.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"They set the record. They must have trained together for a long time.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Well we're a temporary team. Wouldn't have been able to learn much from it anyway.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Well, it's been ten years... I wonder how that team's doing now.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Ah, the relay order... It used to be decided by the captain...","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Then... General, can you decide it for us?","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Alright... in that case, I think Ganquan would be perfect as the first runner!","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"You've always been the first runner during our training. Surely you'll make a good start!","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Hmm... As for General Jiyan and {PlayerName}, I think...","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"General, can you be the connecting third runner? Since you're familiar with both {PlayerName} and us Midnight Rangers.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080}]}